&lt;p&gt;&amp;gt;&#160; RFC-3986: the scheme and host are case-insensitive and therefore should&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;gt;&#160; be normalized to lowercase.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thank you for reporting the issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
